{"tid":1163588,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"看衰郭台銘選情　黎智英：很難想像一個在中國有上百萬員工的商人  會為台灣民主向中國抗議","createTime":"2019-05-20T13:57:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T14:56:05.000Z","uid":35790,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"590c43ebed9b6e4b607fd8cc555c95291b3a2ee0","tid":1163588,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:57:06.000Z","msg":"看衰郭台銘選情　黎智英：很難想像他會為台灣民主向中國抗議<br />\n<br />\n 2019年05月20日<br />\n<br />\n香港外國記者會（The Foreign Correspondents' Club，簡稱FCC）20日下午舉辦午餐會，邀請「壹傳媒」創辦人黎智英演講。黎智英談到傳媒現況和轉型、六四事件、將可能修訂的《逃犯條例》、美中貿易戰，以及對鴻海董事長郭台銘參選台灣總統的看法，對此，<span style=\"color: red;\">黎智英直言不看好郭台銘參選，「很難想像一個在中國有上百萬員工的商人，會為了民主站出來向中國抗議，就像在中國做生意的香港商人，沒人會想站出來為香港民主奮戰。」</span><br />\n<br />\n 但黎智英也說，雖不看好郭台銘選情，但也很難說，「也許台灣人因為經濟長期不景氣，會因為想讓生活變好而不在乎民主。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=63665\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fnews_info.php%3FSerialNo%3D63665&d=RsYziF%2F%2FwXRI7aJQ3s5lGRY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=f59c9eec\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=63665</a>"},{"pid":"beabeb904b7acdd9dc8b6cde9e7bf346125b38ee","tid":1163588,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:57:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de03e2ada6959389c16d47e0b85a4a3dc03221af","tid":1163588,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T13:59:26.000Z","msg":"所以咪撤資搬返去台灣囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae1d15aec494bf699d839f3ee16a0206add3a31","tid":1163588,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T14:56:05.000Z","msg":"血汗工廠"}]}